data.text:
Pittsburgh, PA — New Orleans rapper Curren$y and Pittsburgh buzzmaker Wiz Khalifa have linked up to bring listeners a brand new, collaborative street album. Featuring reader-approved track “Car Service,” the emcees’ brand new How Fly mixtape is available for free download at the link below!
